    "custom_liquid_WphFpm": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Transformaciones realss",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .mx-tf__cases {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 0;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__case {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 0;\n    border-top: 1px solid var(--mx-border);\n    padding: 56px 0;\n    align-items: start;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__case:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mx-border); }\n  .mx-tf__photos {\n    position: relative;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 6px;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__photo {\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    aspect-ratio: 3/4;\n    background: var(--mx-border);\n  }\n  .mx-tf__photo img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    object-position: center 15%;\n    display: block;\n    transition: transform 0.4s ease;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__photo:hover img { transform: scale(1.03); }\n  .mx-tf__photo-badge {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    background: var(--mx-heading);\n    color: var(--mx-gold);\n    font-size: 9px;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    letter-spacing: 0.3em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 8px 0;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__content {\n    padding: 8px 0 0 52px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__case-num {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    letter-spacing: 0.3em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: var(--mx-gold);\n    margin: 0 0 14px;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__case-title {\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-display);\n    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 36px);\n    letter-spacing: 0.04em;\n    color: var(--mx-heading);\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    line-height: 1.0;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__desc {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.85;\n    color: var(--mx-text);\n    margin: 0 0 24px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__quote {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: var(--mx-text-soft);\n    line-height: 1.8;\n    margin: 0 0 12px;\n    padding-left: 16px;\n    border-left: 2px solid var(--mx-gold);\n  }\n  .mx-tf__author {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: var(--mx-heading);\n    font-weight: 500;\n    letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n  .mx-tf__cta {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 56px;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 760px) {\n    .mx-tf__case {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 28px;\n      padding: 40px 0;\n    }\n    .mx-tf__content { padding: 0; }\n    .mx-tf__case-title { font-size: 26px; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"mx-section mx-section--alt\">\n  <div class=\"mx-section__inner mx-section__inner--narrow\">\n\n    <div class=\"mx-section__head\">\n      <p class=\"mx-eyebrow\">Resultados verificados</p>\n      <h2 class=\"mx-title\">Transformaciones <span class=\"mx-title__accent\">reales</span></h2>\n      <p class=\"mx-subtitle\">Resultados reales. Historias reales.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mx-tf__cases\">\n\n      {% assign c1_antes = \"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/3904/5282/files/3_3d83e4dc-f578-4bf2-879a-6554d4969d21.jpg?v=1771954501\" %}\n      {% assign c1_despues = \"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/3904/5282/files/4_7553951e-05f2-4047-9793-795266ec90d1.jpg?v=1771954501\" %}\n      <div class=\"mx-tf__case\">\n        <div class=\"mx-tf__photos\">\n          <div class=\"mx-tf__photo\">\n            <img src=\"{{ c1_antes }}\" alt=\"Antes caso 1\" loading=\"lazy\">\n            <span class=\"mx-tf__photo-badge\">Antes</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"mx-tf__photo\">\n            <img src=\"{{ c1_despues }}\" alt=\"Después caso 1\" loading=\"lazy\">\n            <span class=\"mx-tf__photo-badge\">Después</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mx-tf__content\">\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__case-num\">Caso 01</p>\n          <h3 class=\"mx-tf__case-title\">De barba casi inexistente a línea definida</h3>\n          <hr class=\"mx-divider\">\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__desc\">Inicio con crecimiento muy limitado en mejillas y laterales. Con uso constante, comienzan a activarse nuevos folículos y la barba empieza a tomar forma y definición visible.</p>\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__quote\">\"Siempre pensé que simplemente no me salía barba. Cuando empecé a ver que se marcaban las primeras líneas, supe que sí era posible.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__author\">— Carlos R.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {% assign c2_antes = \"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/3904/5282/files/1_a287d9ae-195f-4d97-81e3-363a0348f189.jpg?v=1771954501\" %}\n      {% assign c2_despues = \"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/3904/5282/files/2_4865bf60-5c9c-43e9-8040-8b2f34b044f5.jpg?v=1771954501\" %}\n      <div class=\"mx-tf__case\">\n        <div class=\"mx-tf__photos\">\n          <div class=\"mx-tf__photo\">\n            <img src=\"{{ c2_antes }}\" alt=\"Antes caso 2\" loading=\"lazy\">\n            <span class=\"mx-tf__photo-badge\">Antes</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"mx-tf__photo\">\n            <img src=\"{{ c2_despues }}\" alt=\"Después caso 2\" loading=\"lazy\">\n            <span class=\"mx-tf__photo-badge\">Después</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mx-tf__content\">\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__case-num\">Caso 02</p>\n          <h3 class=\"mx-tf__case-title\">De zonas vacías a crecimiento visible</h3>\n          <hr class=\"mx-divider\">\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__desc\">Barba prácticamente ausente en áreas clave del rostro. Con constancia, el vello empieza a aparecer donde antes no crecía, logrando una apariencia mucho más completa.</p>\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__quote\">\"Antes tenía zonas totalmente vacías. Ver cómo empezó a salir vello donde no había nada fue lo que más me motivó.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__author\">— Miguel A.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {% assign c3_antes = \"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/3904/5282/files/5_574cabdd-a52b-4ed5-8da1-4bd4e65aad23.jpg?v=1771954501\" %}\n      {% assign c3_despues = \"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/3904/5282/files/6_9f45af40-3bf5-403e-98e0-2a1386ebc47c.jpg?v=1771954501\" %}\n      <div class=\"mx-tf__case\">\n        <div class=\"mx-tf__photos\">\n          <div class=\"mx-tf__photo\">\n            <img src=\"{{ c3_antes }}\" alt=\"Antes caso 3\" loading=\"lazy\">\n            <span class=\"mx-tf__photo-badge\">Antes</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"mx-tf__photo\">\n            <img src=\"{{ c3_despues }}\" alt=\"Después caso 3\" loading=\"lazy\">\n            <span class=\"mx-tf__photo-badge\">Después</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mx-tf__content\">\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__case-num\">Caso 03</p>\n          <h3 class=\"mx-tf__case-title\">De vello fino y disperso a barba con carácter</h3>\n          <hr class=\"mx-divider\">\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__desc\">Inicio con vello muy ligero y sin estructura. Con el tiempo, el crecimiento se vuelve más notorio, la forma se define y la barba adquiere mayor presencia.</p>\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__quote\">\"Yo casi no tenía barba. Ahora ya se ve formada y con más carácter. La diferencia es clara.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"mx-tf__author\">— Adrián M.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mx-tf__cta\">\n      <a href=\"#Tag-Comprar\" class=\"mx-btn mx-btn--primary\">Quiero mi transformación · 30 días sin riesgo →</a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
        "custom_class": ""
      }
    },
    "mx_loox_photos_widget": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"mx-section mx-section--alt\">\n  <div class=\"mx-section__inner\">\n\n    <div class=\"mx-section__head\">\n      <p class=\"mx-eyebrow\">Reseñas con foto</p>\n      <h2 class=\"mx-title\">Más de <span class=\"mx-title__accent\">700 hombres</span><br>ya lo lograron</h2>\n      <p class=\"mx-subtitle\">Reseñas reales con foto de clientes verificados.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    {%- comment -%}\n      Loox standard reviews widget.\n      Detects product context: usa product.id si estamos en una página de producto,\n      si no, usa el bálsamo destacado como fallback (homepage).\n    {%- endcomment -%}\n\n    {%- assign loox_product = product -%}\n    {%- unless loox_product -%}\n      {%- assign loox_product = all_products['1-balsamo-de-minoxidil-al-20-4-oz-crecimiento-de-barba-y-bigote-extra-fuerte-cierra-huecos'] -%}\n    {%- endunless -%}\n\n    <div class=\"mx-loox-reviews\">\n      <div\n        id=\"looxReviews\"\n        data-product-id=\"{{ loox_product.id }}\"\n        class=\"loox-reviews-default\"\n      ></div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .mx-loox-reviews {\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    max-width: 1180px;\n    width: 100%;\n    min-height: 200px;\n  }\n\n  /* Loox widget normalization to brand */\n  .mx-loox-reviews #looxReviews,\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-reviews-default,\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-reviews-wrapper {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: transparent;\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-body) !important;\n  }\n\n  /* Stars → brand gold */\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-icons-star,\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-stars svg,\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-star\"] {\n    color: var(--mx-gold) !important;\n    fill: var(--mx-gold) !important;\n  }\n\n  /* Review cards → brand background */\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-review,\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-review-row,\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-review-card\"] {\n    background: var(--mx-bg-card) !important;\n    border: 1px solid var(--mx-border) !important;\n    border-radius: 4px !important;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(26,24,20,0.05) !important;\n    transition: border-color 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;\n  }\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-review:hover,\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-review-row:hover {\n    border-color: var(--mx-gold) !important;\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(184,154,82,0.12) !important;\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n  }\n\n  /* Photos in reviews */\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-photo,\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-photo\"] img,\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-thumbnails img {\n    border-radius: 4px !important;\n    border: 1px solid var(--mx-border);\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;\n  }\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-photo:hover,\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-photo\"]:hover img {\n    transform: scale(1.03);\n    border-color: var(--mx-gold);\n  }\n\n  /* Author + text colors */\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-author,\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-author\"],\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-name\"] {\n    color: var(--mx-heading) !important;\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-text,\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-text\"],\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-body\"] {\n    color: var(--mx-text) !important;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n  }\n\n  /* Pagination/buttons → brand */\n  .mx-loox-reviews button,\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-button,\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"loox-pagination\"] button {\n    color: var(--mx-heading) !important;\n    border-color: var(--mx-gold) !important;\n  }\n  .mx-loox-reviews button:hover {\n    background: var(--mx-gold) !important;\n    color: var(--mx-heading) !important;\n  }\n\n  /* Remove \"Submit a review\" button color clash */\n  .mx-loox-reviews .loox-write-review,\n  .mx-loox-reviews [class*=\"write-review-button\"] {\n    background: var(--mx-heading) !important;\n    color: var(--mx-gold) !important;\n    border: none !important;\n    border-radius: 2px !important;\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-body) !important;\n    letter-spacing: 0.12em !important;\n    text-transform: uppercase !important;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n  (function() {\n    function nudgeLoox() {\n      if (window.loox && typeof window.loox.refresh === 'function') {\n        try { window.loox.refresh(); } catch (e) {}\n      }\n    }\n    if (document.readyState === 'loading') {\n      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', nudgeLoox);\n    } else {\n      nudgeLoox();\n    }\n  })();\n</script>",
        "custom_class": ""
      }
    },
    "mx_como_funciona": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .mx-hw__grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 24px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .mx-hw__step {\n    position: relative;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--mx-border);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 40px 28px 32px;\n    text-align: center;\n    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n  }\n  .mx-hw__step:hover {\n    border-color: var(--mx-gold);\n    transform: translateY(-4px);\n    box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(184,154,82,0.15);\n  }\n  .mx-hw__num {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: -22px;\n    left: 50%;\n    transform: translateX(-50%);\n    width: 44px;\n    height: 44px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: var(--mx-heading);\n    color: var(--mx-gold);\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-display);\n    font-size: 22px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.04em;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    border: 3px solid var(--mx-bg-alt);\n  }\n  .mx-hw__icon {\n    width: 56px;\n    height: 56px;\n    margin: 8px auto 22px;\n    color: var(--mx-gold);\n  }\n  .mx-hw__icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; stroke-width: 1.4; }\n  .mx-hw__title {\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-display);\n    font-size: 26px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.05em;\n    color: var(--mx-heading);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    line-height: 1;\n    margin: 0 0 14px;\n  }\n  .mx-hw__text {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    color: var(--mx-text);\n    margin: 0 0 18px;\n  }\n  .mx-hw__time {\n    display: inline-block;\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-display);\n    font-size: 13px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.18em;\n    color: var(--mx-gold);\n    padding: 6px 14px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--mx-gold-soft);\n    border-radius: 100px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n  }\n  .mx-hw__connector {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 50%;\n    right: -16px;\n    transform: translateY(-50%);\n    width: 28px;\n    color: var(--mx-gold);\n    z-index: 2;\n  }\n  .mx-hw__step:last-child .mx-hw__connector { display: none; }\n  .mx-hw__cta {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 48px;\n  }\n  .mx-hw__note {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 18px;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: var(--mx-text-soft);\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 760px) {\n    .mx-hw__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }\n    .mx-hw__connector { display: none; }\n    .mx-hw__step { padding: 36px 22px 28px; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"mx-section\">\n  <div class=\"mx-section__inner mx-section__inner--md\">\n\n    <div class=\"mx-section__head\">\n      <p class=\"mx-eyebrow\">Cómo funciona</p>\n      <h2 class=\"mx-title\">Tu transformación en <span class=\"mx-title__accent\">3 pasos</span></h2>\n      <p class=\"mx-subtitle\">Sin clínicas. Sin trasplantes. Sin promesas vacías. Solo constancia y la fórmula correcta.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mx-hw__grid\">\n\n      <div class=\"mx-hw__step\">\n        <div class=\"mx-hw__num\">1</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-hw__icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M9 11l3 3L22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-hw__title\">Aplica</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-hw__text\">1ml en la zona de la barba, dos veces al día. Mañana y noche, sobre piel limpia y seca.</p>\n        <span class=\"mx-hw__time\">~ 2 min al día</span>\n        <div class=\"mx-hw__connector\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 28 14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M0 7h26m0 0L20 1m6 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-hw__step\">\n        <div class=\"mx-hw__num\">2</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-hw__icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-hw__title\">Activa</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-hw__text\">El minoxidil 20% despierta los folículos durmientes. Al inicio aparece vello fino — es la señal de que está funcionando.</p>\n        <span class=\"mx-hw__time\">Semanas 1 a 4</span>\n        <div class=\"mx-hw__connector\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 28 14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M0 7h26m0 0L20 1m6 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-hw__step\">\n        <div class=\"mx-hw__num\">3</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-hw__icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n            <path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-hw__title\">Define</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-hw__text\">El vello se engrosa, llena los huecos y la barba toma forma. Para resultados completos: 6 meses de uso constante.</p>\n        <span class=\"mx-hw__time\">Semana 8 en adelante</span>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mx-hw__cta\">\n      <a href=\"#Tag-Comprar\" class=\"mx-btn mx-btn--primary\">Empezar mi tratamiento →</a>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"mx-hw__note\">Constancia es la clave. La fórmula es seria, no es magia.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
        "custom_class": ""
      }
    },
