      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .mx-bn__grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));\n    gap: 16px;\n    margin-bottom: 56px;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__item {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: 20px 24px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--mx-border);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(26,24,20,0.04);\n    transition: border-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;\n    gap: 14px;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__item:hover {\n    border-color: var(--mx-gold);\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(184,154,82,0.18);\n    transform: translateY(-3px);\n  }\n  .mx-bn__item-icon {\n    width: 40px;\n    height: 40px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    color: var(--mx-heading);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__item-icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; stroke-width: 1.5; }\n  .mx-bn__item-icon--solid {\n    background: var(--mx-gold);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    width: 38px;\n    height: 38px;\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-display);\n    letter-spacing: 0.05em;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__item-text {\n    flex: 1;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    color: var(--mx-heading);\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__check {\n    width: 22px;\n    height: 22px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    color: var(--mx-gold);\n  }\n  .mx-bn__check svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; stroke: currentColor; stroke-width: 3; }\n\n  .mx-bn__detailed {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));\n    gap: 24px;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__card {\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 36px 24px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--mx-border);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(26,24,20,0.04);\n    transition: border-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    height: 100%;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__card:hover {\n    border-color: var(--mx-gold);\n    box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(184,154,82,0.18);\n    transform: translateY(-4px);\n  }\n  .mx-bn__card-icon {\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    margin: 0 auto 22px;\n    color: var(--mx-gold);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__card-icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; stroke-width: 1.4; }\n  .mx-bn__card-icon--solid {\n    background: var(--mx-gold);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    width: 48px;\n    height: 48px;\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-display);\n    letter-spacing: 0.05em;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__card-title {\n    font-family: var(--mx-font-display);\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: var(--mx-heading);\n    margin: 0 0 12px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n  }\n  .mx-bn__card-text {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: var(--mx-text);\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0;\n    flex-grow: 1;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"mx-section mx-section--white\">\n  <div class=\"mx-section__inner mx-section__inner--md\">\n\n    <div class=\"mx-section__head\">\n      <p class=\"mx-eyebrow\">Beneficios</p>\n      <h2 class=\"mx-title\">Esto es lo que <span class=\"mx-title__accent\">Maximus Inc</span> hará por ti</h2>\n      <p class=\"mx-subtitle\">Diseñado para hombres que buscan resultados reales sin complicaciones.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mx-bn__grid\">\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__item\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/><path d=\"M12 8v8\"/><path d=\"M8 12h8\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-text\">Sin irritación ni resequedad</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__check\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17L4 12\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__item\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-icon mx-bn__item-icon--solid\">4</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-text\">Primeros resultados en 4 semanas</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__check\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17L4 12\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__item\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-text\">Absorción TOTAL en 2 minutos</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__check\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17L4 12\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__item\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M9 21h6v-2h-6v2zm3-19C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12c0 2.8 1.15 5.33 3 7.11V21h2v-2.24c2.06 1.47 4.51 2.24 7 2.24s4.94-.77 7-2.24V21h2v-1.89c1.85-1.78 3-4.31 3-7.11 0-5.52-4.48-10-10-10zm3.5 13c0 1.93-1.57 3.5-3.5 3.5s-3.5-1.57-3.5-3.5 1.57-3.5 3.5-3.5 3.5 1.57 3.5 3.5z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-text\">No se nota que lo traes puesto</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__check\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17L4 12\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__item\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"/><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"/><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"/><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-text\">Acompañamiento 1 a 1</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__check\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17L4 12\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__item\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__item-text\">Fácil & rápido de utilizar</div>\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__check\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17L4 12\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mx-bn__detailed\">\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__card\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__card-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20.24 12.24a6 6 0 0 0-8.49-8.49L5 10.5V19h8.5z\"/><line x1=\"16\" y1=\"8\" x2=\"2\" y2=\"22\"/><line x1=\"17.5\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"15\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-bn__card-title\">Sin Irritación ni Resequedad</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-bn__card-text\">A diferencia de otros tratamientos que tienen estos efectos secundarios. Nuestra fórmula cuida de tu piel mientras estimula el crecimiento de tu barba.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__card\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__card-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-bn__card-title\">Absorción Total en 2 minutos</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-bn__card-text\">Una vez aplicado se absorbe completamente en solo 2 minutos. Sigue con tu día sin residuos ni sensación pegajosa.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__card\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__card-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"/><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"/><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"/><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-bn__card-title\">Acompañamiento 1 a 1</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-bn__card-text\">Tu éxito es nuestra prioridad. Acompañamiento personalizado en cada paso para asegurar los mejores resultados.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__card\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__card-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M2.5 17a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0-10 2 2 0 0 1 1.4-1.4 49.56 49.56 0 0 1 16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 21.5 7a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0 10 2 2 0 0 1-1.4 1.4 49.55 49.55 0 0 1-16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 2.5 17\"/><path d=\"m10 15 5-3-5-3z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-bn__card-title\">Máxima Discreción</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-bn__card-text\">Diseñado para hombres que valoran la privacidad. Se absorbe sin dejar rastros, asegurando que nadie note que lo estás utilizando.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__card\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__card-icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-bn__card-title\">Fácil & Rápido</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-bn__card-text\">Sabemos que eres un hombre ocupado. Diseñado para que lo apliques en menos de 3 minutos.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"mx-bn__card\">\n        <div class=\"mx-bn__card-icon mx-bn__card-icon--solid\">4</div>\n        <h3 class=\"mx-bn__card-title\">Bienvenido a la familia</h3>\n        <p class=\"mx-bn__card-text\">En 4 semanas, te darás cuenta de que HOY tomaste una buena decisión.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
